# Turret
placements.entities.HonlyHelper/Turret.tooltips.turretID=The ID of the turret for use with the Turret Controller.
placements.entities.HonlyHelper/Turret.tooltips.aimTime=How long the turret should spend reading the player's movement before shooting.
placements.entities.HonlyHelper/Turret.tooltips.cooldownTime=How long the turret should sit and wait after shooting.
