placements.triggers.HonlyHelper/GothTattle.tooltips.DialogAmount=The amount of dialogs you have that start with the GothDialogID.
placements.triggers.HonlyHelper/GothTattle.tooltips.Loops=Whether the dialog should repeat from the first entry after playing the last one.
placements.triggers.HonlyHelper/GothTattle.tooltips.Ends=Whether the trigger should disable after playing the last entry.

