placements.triggers.HonlyHelper/TurretController.tooltips.turretID=The ID of the turret you want to affect.
placements.triggers.HonlyHelper/TurretController.tooltips.turretAction=The action that the turret needs to do. Use the "GunOnly" options if you don't want helicopter sounds. Note: HeliFadeIn takes a long time to fade in (20 seconds roughly).
